1057
01:57:11,000 --> 01:57:28,500
So if they can't show that this is the most efficient way to do it, then the site evaluation committee could say, well, we're not going to give you a certificate until you do that.

1058
01:57:28,500 --> 01:57:38,000
I'm sure the utilities are going to fight like hell, but I think, again, this is billions of dollars.

1059
01:57:38,000 --> 01:57:46,000
And I don't know how many people have been looked at transmission projects in the past.

1060
01:57:46,000 --> 01:57:54,500
