02:03:40,500 --> 02:03:46,500
I'm currently chairing a commission to study the assessing of power generation.

1099
02:03:46,500 --> 02:04:00,000
It's been a very difficult and contentious subject in our state, because we have the Department of Revenue Administration assessing generation plants for the utility property tax.

1100
02:04:00,000 --> 02:04:08,000
